ge","time":"May 15, 2024 12:46 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😮"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"When that uncle did all those things and my father was like I will go so he told those guys that he might come but one of the person who he told called my dad and was like your brother is saying all this","time":"May 15, 2024 12:47 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"So he went and it was a scene","time":"May 15, 2024 12:47 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"That’s pretty evil of the uncle","time":"May 15, 2024 12:48 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yuppp","time":"May 15, 2024 12:48 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Was your father fine sir","time":"May 15, 2024 12:48 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Like he helped him when he had nothing and he did all these things so it was bad","time":"May 15, 2024 12:48 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yuppp","time":"May 15, 2024 12:48 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I will tell you one incident","time":"May 15, 2024 12:49 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Right","time":"May 15, 2024 12:49 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yeppp","time":"May 15, 2024 12:49 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"So once one of my fathers sister was getting married at that time he was in Mumbai and didn’t go home for many years so he was like will go this time for marriage. At that time i used to live with my Mamu . So he came to the village and we were going in a car to the wedding. The road was like very deserted. And after sometime someone started following our car for some distance","time":"May 15, 2024 12:51 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"That was scary","time":"May 15, 2024 12:51 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yupppp","time":"May 15, 2024 12:52 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Must have been","time":"May 15, 2024 12:52 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yes’s","time":"May 15, 2024 12:52 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Did you know about these in childhood sir","time":"May 15, 2024 12:53 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"No one told but I could guessAnd I spent very less time as a child with him like until 10th I don’t even remember a full day with him","time":"May 15, 2024 12:54 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"But I knew something was wrong","time":"May 15, 2024 12:54 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"That was not a good time","time":"May 15, 2024 12:54 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I know","time":"May 15, 2024 12:54 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Everybody has their own kind off past they don’t like","time":"May 15, 2024 12:55 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Right","time":"May 15, 2024 12:55 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"He’s changed after coming here","time":"May 15, 2024 12:56 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Only me and my sister remember bits of it","time":"May 15, 2024 12:56 pm","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"You got good memory","time":"May 15, 2024 12:56 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"😁","time":"May 15, 2024 12:56 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"😁","time":"May 15, 2024 12:57 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"The downside is I remember some traumatising stuff too","time":"May 15, 2024 12:57 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yep","time":"May 15, 2024 12:57 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"They don’t leave too","time":"May 15, 2024 12:57 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yes’s","time":"May 15, 2024 12:57 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","te